(620, 1, '2018-08-14 04:48:50', '2018-08-14 04:48:50', '<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5\"><img src=\"http://localhost/investments/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/author.png\">\r\n<h3>About the Author</h3><h4>Andreas Thalassinos (BSc, MSc, MSTA, CFTe, MFTA)</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7\">\r\n<p>FXTMs Head of Education is a highly respected FX educator and Certified Technical Analyst. Andreas Thalassinos is known around the world as an authority on algorithmic trading, and has developed hundreds of the automated systems, indicators and trading tools used by FXTM traders.\r\n\r\nHis passion for educating traders and Forex industry professionals has made him a Guru in the industry, and his tutorials are well received across the globe by thousands of attendees on a regular basis. Now, Mr. Thalassinos has infused his renowned enthusiasm and engaging analytical breakdowns into his very own series of Ebooks.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><!-- row-->\r\n<hr class=\"edu-hr\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\" style=\"background-color:black\">\r\n<img  src=\"http://localhost/investments/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bearish-mock-up.png\" style=\"margin-top:10px;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color:white!important\">Bearish Japanese Candlesticks & Strategie</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;color:white\">A guide to understanding and applying one of the most popular and trusted technical charting tools in forex - the Japanese Candlestick. The second part of our mini-series on candlestick formations looks closely at bearish patterns and strategies. Download it for free today!</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:white\">\r\nBearish Japanese Candlesticks & Strategies covers:\r\n<ul style=\"color:white\">\r\n<li>The value of reading and using candlestick patterns for traders</li>\r\n<li>Integration of candlestick charting into trading strategies</li>\r\n<li>Visual examples of charts and formations</li>\r\n<li>And much more!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</p>\r\n<c