(1101, 1, '2018-08-23 09:55:30', '2018-08-23 09:55:30', '<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"row article-info\">\r\n<h3>Expand your knowledge of forex trading with FXTMs educational articles. Written by our experts, this series has been designed to provide traders at all levels with the skills and knowledge they need to trade with confidence.</h3>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost/investments/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/author.png\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\r\n<p>Andreas Thalassinos (BSc, MSc, MSTA, CFTe, MFTA) is a renowned forex educator. FXTMs Head of Education and a Certified Technical Analyst, whose automated systems, tools and indicators are used around the world by traders, investors, brokers and investment firms.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><!--row1-->\r\n<hr class=\"edu-hr\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost/investments/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/BlockRewards_1140x570_cover-1.jpg\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7\">\r\n<h2>Bitcoin Block Rewards</h2>\r\n<p><b>Andreas Thalassinos</b></p>\r\n<p>Proof-of-work is one of the more brilliant features of Satoshi Nakamotos innovation, Bitcoin. It represents the confirmation of transactions or, more specifically, blocks of transactions.</p>\r\n<center><button class=\"edu-btn\">Read</button></center>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><!--row2-->\r\n<hr class=\"edu-hr\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost/investments/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/BlockChain_1140x570_cover-1.jpg\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7\">\r\n<h2>Blockchains: Mining for bitcoins</h2>\r\n<p><b>Andreas Thalassinos</b></p>\r\n<p>Blockchain technology is at the heart of cryptocurrencies, including the most famous one of all - bitcoin. In its simplest form, a blockchain consists of blocks of information.</p>\r\n<center><button class=\"edu-btn\">Read</button></center>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><!--row3-->\r\n<hr class=\"edu-hr\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost/investments/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Cryptocurrency_Wallets_1140x570_cover.jpg\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7\">\r\n<h2>Cryptocurrency Wallets</h2>\r\n<p><b>Andreas Thalassinos</b></p>\r\n<p>A cryptocurrency wallet is a medium that stores your private and public key, and allows you to receive and send digital coins.</p>\r\n<center><button class=\"edu-btn\">Read</button></center>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><!--row4-->\r\n<hr class=\"edu-hr\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost/investments/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Bitcoin_Transactions_1140x570_03-1.jpg\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7\">\r\n<h2>Uncovering Bitcoin Transactions: How they Work</h2>\r\n<p><b>Andreas Thalassinos</b></p>\r\n<p>A bitcoin transaction is a signed piece of information for the purpose of transferring ownership of a set amount of bitcoins from one individual to another.</p>\r\n<center><button class=\"edu-btn\">Read</button></center>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><!--row5-->\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-5\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost/investments/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1_Bitcoin_Origin_1140x570.jpg\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-7\">\r\n<h2>The Origins of the Digital Currency: A Beginning of a Long New Road</h2>\r\n<p><b>Andreas Thalassinos</b></p>\r\n<p>A crypIn recent times, especially after the 2008 financial crisis, we all became more familiar with financial terms such as bail-in and bailout and those of us who are not economists realised that the heart of a countrys economy beats in its local financial institutions and banks.</p>\r\n<center><button class=\"edu-btn\">Read</button></center>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><!--row6-->\r\n<hr class=\"edu-hr\">\r\n\r\n</div><!--section-->', 'Education Articles', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '626-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-23 09:55:30', '2018-08-23 09:55:30', '', 626, 'http://localhost/investments/201